dc_description_s: This polygon data layer represents municipalities for Waupaca County, Wisconsin in 2015. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, Waupaca_Municipalities_2015.gdb. [The data set represents the jurisdictional boundaries for the various units of local government within Waupaca County, Wisconsin. The data is represented using polygons stored in a Geodatabase. The data is updated annually.]
uw_supplemental_s: Augmented original metadata with UW-Madison specific elements. Best available date of this dataset is 5/12/2015. For online dataset download, please visit http://www.co.waupaca.wi.us/landinformation/Data.aspx
